CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `recordings` (
            `id` INTEGER PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL, 
            `mbid` TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL, 
            `title` TEXT NOT NULL, 
            `length` INTEGER, 
            `disambiguation` TEXT, 
            `annotation` TEXT,

            -- Foreign keys
            `artist_credit` INTEGER REFERENCES `artist_credits`(`id`)
        ) STRICT;
